# =====================================================
# WHAT WORKS WITHOUT SUPABASE?
# =====================================================
# ✅ Dashboard and all UI components
# ✅ Cases management (in-memory, no persistence)
# ✅ First Call workflow
# ✅ Appointments scheduling
# ✅ All navigation and views
#
# ❌ Logo upload (requires Supabase Storage)
# ❌ eSignatures (requires Supabase + HelloSign)
# ❌ Database persistence
# ❌ Real-time updates
# =====================================================

# =====================================================
# QUICK START
# =====================================================
# 1. Copy this file:
#    cp env.example .env
#
# 2. App will work immediately (no Supabase needed)
#
# 3. When ready for full features:
#    - Create Supabase account (free)
#    - Uncomment VITE_SUPABASE_* lines above
#    - Fill in your actual keys
#    - Restart: npm run dev
#
# 4. For production deployment:
#    Add all variables in your hosting dashboard
# =====================================================

